Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,唱一个 小真鹤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.44,0:15:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,唱一个 唱一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.18,0:16:08.91,Top,,0,0,0,,唱一个 唱一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.68,0:15:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,果然 就知道他们会整点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不好 他要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.66,0:16:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,润平?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你们 跟我来办公室!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.50,0:16:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,2年级1班所有人跟我去办公室!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,流莺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,森同学 下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,真好 可以下台了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,有那么点搞笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 他要转到什么时候?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害 那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.90,0:17:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.51,0:17:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,「海盗」里的Ali吧 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.51,0:17:27.96,Cmt,,0,0,0,,注：芭蕾舞剧「海盗 (Le Corsaire)」，Act II - 4. Grand Pas: Variation: Ali。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,海盗? Ali?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,芭蕾舞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,诶? 芭蕾?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,笑死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,五代家是开芭蕾舞教室的来着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,即便如此 一般也不会这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.64,0:17:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,芭蕾? 为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是男生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.32,0:17:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧 润平?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,诶…? 不是吧 为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.28,0:17:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,该死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,流莺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚才看起来很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.72,0:18:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就像以前跳芭蕾的时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不止 比以前还要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 这么快就要回家?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.68,0:18:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,再跳一次吧 我要录下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.46,0:18:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,紧身裤也给你买好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,穿上这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我们去社团活动室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这是长筒袜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.77,0:18:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 润平
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.58,0:18:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,别套头上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:18:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,别找他了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我来给你们跳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.25,0:19:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,有点像了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.72,0:19:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你模仿得还真快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:09.04,Top,,0,0,0,,这脸…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我也在学芭蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.24,0:19:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.73,0:19:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才那家伙很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我讨厌他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你们要是开他的玩笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.71,0:19:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我受不了 很难受 很丢人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.92,0:19:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我芭蕾跳得很烂…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,可我想要进步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.60,0:19:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我要退出足球部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.32,0:19:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,也没办法和阿兵组成乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,搞不懂 你这突然说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,并不突然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直想跳芭蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己也不明白为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可我总是无法忘记芭蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直想把那感觉当作是错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾想要让大家看到阳刚的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.53,0:20:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,阳刚也好…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.14,0:20:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,帅气也好…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,其实就是贯彻真正的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.59,0:20:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要认真学习芭蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.34,0:20:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我若是有了芭蕾 受到嘲笑又何妨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.34,0:20:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,阿兵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 够气人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他没时间陪我们这些混在烂足球部的人玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的 不是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.83,0:20:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,润平
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.11,0:20:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,要我说 真搞不懂你为什么喜欢芭蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.94,0:20:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,而你这还要退出足球部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉好怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.14,0:21:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,哟 这是哪位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我要报警了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.26,0:21:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,等下 老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不…老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.03,0:21:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,请教我芭蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.41,0:21:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.52,0:21:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里有王子理光头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:22:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.23,0:23:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,停不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.74,0:23:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,停下来 我会死
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.51,0:23:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,舞动不止 第4幕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.01,0:23:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以跳芭蕾了
